content: This has been in the works for the past few months actually. And we've been texting on discord for an month actually.

We don't use discord to text. Discord is like slack.
You said in your response "we've been texting on discord for an month actually." Confusion here.

Let's hope I can get over myself cuz it's pretty weird for me and my wife and we've been doing this since the beginning. I'll check in when my frustrations settle down. Thanks for engaging! Have a good day!
